            "row_content": "<p>As soon as your order is dispatched, you'll receive a dispatch email with delivery dates and details for your order.<br/><br/>If you require an update on your order, you can email <a href=\"mailto:customerservice@i4lgroup.co.uk\" title=\"mailto:customerservice@i4lgroup.co.uk\">customerservice@i4lgroup.co.uk</a> with your order number for assistance.</p>",
