            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes, if you are carrying out a construction project that requires a large quantity of materials, email <a href=\"mailto:sales@i4lgroup.co.uk\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mailto:sales@i4lgroup.co.uk\">sales@i4lgroup.co.uk</a> with the following information and we will get back to you with your very own bespoke price quote:</p><ul><li>Delivery postcode and address</li><li>Mobile number</li><li>Company name</li><li>A list of required materials and their quantities</li></ul><p>Learn more on <a href=\"/pages/tiles4less-online-trade-with-marketfinance\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Tiles4Less Online Trade\">opening a trade account</a>.<br/></p>",
            "page": ""
