            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes, if your order has not yet been processed for dispatch, cancellation/ amendments should be possible.<br/><br/>Our team works quickly to get your order delivered as soon as possible so it is likely that your order will be processed for dispatch within 2-3 hours of purchase.<br/><br/>Contact us immediately via <a href=\"mailto:customerservice@i4lgroup.co.uk\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mailto:customerservice@i4lgroup.co.uk\">customerservice@i4lgroup.co.uk</a> or call <a href=\"tel:020-3481-1978\">020-4571-0589</a> during opening hours.<br/><br/>If you wish to amend your order after it has been processed by our team, it will be treated as a return or a separate new order.<br/><br/>Read more: <a href=\"/pages/returns\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"/pages/returns\">Returns</a></p>",
